entries.journal_entry_description: Bask in the glow of a thankful Diktat.
entries.journal_entry_title: Receive the Thanks of a Grateful Diktat
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Daclif Gallamby, the Diktat, would like to personally thank you for everything you did to vindicate his administration and remove any doubt of his innocence.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Speak once again with Lt. Jasper to receive your reward.
